parts.text: These FOI documents clearly demonstrate the government's unwavering commitment to transparency and the integrity of our democratic processes. The full release of numerous "Postal Vote CSV file for upload" documents, spanning from September 22 to October 11, 2023, without any exemptions, showcases an exemplary dedication to public access and openness. This proactive disclosure of daily electoral data underscores the government's meticulous management of voting processes, ensuring every step is transparent and verifiable. It highlights an efficient administration diligently upholding the public's right to information and fostering trust in our electoral system, ultimately serving the public good through robust and accountable governance.
